data.description:
Don't miss out on this adorable North Portland bungalow! Two bedrooms with one bath give you plenty of space to enjoy, with stylish hardwood floors, ceiling fans, tile bath surround, and fantastic wood counters in the kitchen! Need more room? Enjoy the basement with included washer/dryer to make chores super easy! Or check out the adorable, wood-paneled attic loft space. Spacious closets in the bedrooms include shelves for easy storage! Need fresh air? Check out the private, fenced backyard with mature trees and paved patio! WE EVEN WELCOME PETS! 

You'll love the quiet, neighborhood setting. It's just steps from McCoy Park and Community Garden, Clarendon Community Garden, Northgate Park and Peninsula Crossing Trail. Easy commuting with nearby Portsmouth Ave, Columbia Blvd,Lombard St and I-5. Just a block from the Bus Line 4 stop! 

KEY FEATURES
Year Built: 1924
